Koolbridge Solar, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 9:35 AM ET
Electrical Equipment

Company Overview of Koolbridge Solar, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Koolbridge Solar, Inc. designs, develops, and sells electrical products that allow solar energy to be integrated into homes. It develops Smart Load Center, a solar and utility energy smart breaker box that can automatically select the use of utility power or solar-derived power independently for each of a number of circuit breakers in a panel box; and solar inverters. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Wrightsville Beach, North Carolina.


