Koolbridge Solar, Inc. Key Developments

Koolbridge Solar Promotes William 'Bill' Griffin as President and CEO
Feb 1 17
William "Bill" Griffin promoted to President and CEO at Koolbridge Solar. Bill brings to Koolbridge Solar an extensive amount of business development, operations, financial analysis, business operations, team building, start-up, partner relationship building, global distribution, and government sales expertise. As President and CEO he has been tasked by the Koolbridge Solar Board of Directors to build the company into the leading global provider of renewable energy solutions. Prior to joining Koolbridge Solar, Bill was an Executive Coach at Cornerstone Advisory Partners.


Koolbridge Solar, Inc. Auditor Raises 'Going Concern' Doubt
Oct 13 16
Koolbridge Solar, Inc. filed its Annual on Oct 13, 2016 for the period ending Dec 31, 2015. In this report its auditor, Daszkal Bolton LLP, gave an unqualified opinion expressing doubt that the company can continue as a going concern.


