Koolbridge Solar Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















koolbridge solar inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Renewable Energy
Sub-Industry: Renewable Energy Equipment
Koolbridge Solar, Inc. designs, develops and sells electrical products. The Company offers solar energy breaker box that can automatically select the use of electrical power from the utility grid, solar panels, batteries, generators, and wind power. Koolbridge Solar operates in the State of North Carolina.




